claim: Dennis Hastert served as a congressman.
premise_source_doc_sentence: John Dennis Hastert  (  -LSB- ˈhæstərt -RSB- born January 2 , 1942  )  is an American former congressman who served as the 51st Speaker of the United States House of Representatives from 1999 to 2007 , representing from 1987 to 2007 .
